      <p>I translate complex technical concepts into accessible outcomes. My specialty is taking engineer-built tools and making them irresistible to broader markets. I move fluidly between development, data science, growth marketing, and business strategy—creating clarity where there was confusion.</p>

      <h2>Let's Build Something Significant</h2>
